title: Laurel & Hardy - Dirty Work 1931(zee)
description:
STORY: 

Chimney Sweeps Laurel and Hardy arrive at the house of Professor Noodle, 
an off-his-nut scientist who has discovered the secret to eternal youth. 
While Stan and Ollie make a shambles of his living room, Prof. Noodle 
excitedly works on his formula. In the end, the Boys go see what all the fuss is about, 
and Stan accidentally knocks Ollie into a vat of the rejuvenating liquid. 
He emerges as a monkey with a derby who\&#039;s only reaction is the oft-repeated \"I have nothing to say\".
